my first time as an adult.

17:44.085 --> 17:45.835
-Yeah, yeah.
-(laughing): Yeah.

17:45.919 --> 17:49.418
-I'll let you have a moment.
-Oh, sure. I'll see you
back in the room.

17:50.919 --> 17:52.460
