under this machine and...

18:12.835 --> 18:14.960
It was hard.
(chuckling)

18:17.001 --> 18:19.460
But, look.

18:19.543 --> 18:22.168
He has tattoos.

18:22.251 --> 18:23.585
-Oh, that's cool.
-Yeah.

18:23.669 --> 18:26.210
