with the radiation machine.

18:26.293 --> 18:33.335
-Hey! Cool party dots, bruh!
-Yeah! (chuckles)

18:40.669 --> 18:43.752
God, have you been outside
today? It's gorgeous.

18:43.835 --> 18:47.251
