19:00.126 --> 19:03.001
of Miss Saigon
and Les Miserables  and...

19:03.085 --> 19:05.919
- RENT  . Yep.
-...and then RENT  , yeah.

19:06.001 --> 19:08.710
-You don't
remember that?
-I do.

19:08.794 --> 19:12.335
You had neon green
rubber bands on your braces,

19:12.418 --> 19:14.335
-and there was a lot of snot.
-There was a lot of snot.

19:14.418 --> 19:16.418
-Yes.
-'Cause I'm a snotty
crier, still am.

19:16.502 --> 19:17.710
(laughing)

19:17.794 --> 19:19.919
