19:21.251 --> 19:24.043
Hey, I was thinking about it
on the ride over here...

19:25.377 --> 19:26.877
We were good friends.

19:26.960 --> 19:29.627
-We were best
friends, yeah.
-Yeah!

19:29.710 --> 19:31.502
Yeah.

19:31.585 --> 19:35.335
Whatever happened
to that friendship?

19:35.418 --> 19:37.627
Well...

19:37.710 --> 19:39.293
You and Bryan would always
do drugs together,

19:39.377 --> 19:41.085
and I didn't want
him to do that.

19:43.085 --> 19:44.585
Fair.

19:45.919 --> 19:47.919
You know, I remember
that I was giving you

19:48.001 --> 19:51.126
-a lot of shit for voting
for Bush the first time...
-Oh my Lord.

19:51.210 --> 19:54.835
-...'cause I couldn't vote yet,
and you were crazy.
-Yes, yes.

19:54.919 --> 19:57.835
And you were really
self-righteous and obnoxious

19:57.919 --> 19:59.835
-about Ralph Nader.
-Ralph Nader!

19:59.919 --> 20:01.669
'Cause he's got
some good ideas.

20:01.752 --> 20:05.126
-You were kind of an
asshole about it, actually.
-I was. That's fair too.

20:06.752 --> 20:08.085
Yeah.

20:10.210 --> 20:13.210
-Did your dad vote for--
-Yeah, of course he did.

20:13.293 --> 20:14.669
Yeah.

20:14.752 --> 20:17.085
-Did you?
-No, I didn't vote.

20:17.168 --> 20:19.794
Okay, okay.

20:26.543 --> 20:28.877
You know why I thought
you were pissed?

20:28.960 --> 20:31.085
-Why?
-The talent show.

20:31.168 --> 20:32.543
What?

20:32.627 --> 20:35.168
