about it my entire life.

20:50.627 --> 20:52.043
What?

20:52.126 --> 20:53.752
-What are you laughing at?
-Are you kidding?

20:53.835 --> 20:56.043
I have no memory of that.

20:56.835 --> 20:58.502
-Really?
-No.

20:58.585 --> 21:00.377
You were so fucking pissed.

21:00.460 --> 21:02.377
Was I? I have
no recollection.

21:02.460 --> 21:05.335
-I've been sweating this
for like 20 years...
-(laughing)

21:05.418 --> 21:07.251
...and you're telling me--
Dude!

21:07.335 --> 21:08.877
You know, I might have
done a lot of drugs,

21:08.960 --> 21:11.001
-but you have
a really shitty memory.
-(baby fussing)

21:11.085 --> 21:13.919
Oh, oh, oh.
Yeah, yeah. Okay.

21:14.001 --> 21:16.168
-Good morning.
-Yeah, hi.

21:16.251 --> 21:19.126
Aww, okay. Yeah?

