23:39.251 --> 23:41.001
None of the "abruhve."

23:41.085 --> 23:43.919
One for me,
one for you.

23:44.001 --> 23:46.585
-I don't have a bike.
-Oh, that's not
a problem, bruh.

23:50.919 --> 23:53.126
(both laughing)

23:58.752 --> 24:00.752
-Look at that!
-Whoa.

